<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389296>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Phanoperla wangi Wang, Li & Li, sp. nov., male. a. Aedeagus, dorsal view. b. Aedeagal sac, dorsolateral view. c. Aedeagal sac, ventral view. d. Aedeagus, lateral view. e. Aedeagal sac, oblique ventral view. Abbreviations: ta: tubular apex. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389296/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389306>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Phanoperla vietnamensis Zwick, 1986, male. a. Aedeagus, lateral view. b. Aedeagus, dorsal view. c. Aedeagus, ventral view. d.Aedeagal sac, ventral view. e.Aedeagal sac, lateral view. f.Aedeagal sac, ventrolateral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389306/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389300>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Phanoperla himalayana Zwick, 1977, male. a. Head and pronotum, dorsal view. b. Aedeagus, ventral view. c. Terminalia, dorsal view. d. Aedeagus, lateral view. Abbreviations: ta: tubular apex; das: dark apical sclerite. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389300/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389312>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Phanoperla Banks, 1938, aedeagus, lateral view. a. Phanoperla wangi Wang, Li & Li, sp. nov.; b. Phanoperla maindroni (Navás, 1926), modified from Zwick (1982); c. Phanoperla vietnamensis Zwick, 1986, modified from Zwick (1986); d. Phanoperla himalayana Zwick, 1977, modified from Zwick (1982); e. Phanoperla wieng Sivec & Stark, 2010, modified from Sivec & Stark (2010). Abbreviations: dls: dorsolateral swellings, fsl: finger-shaped lobe; ta: tubular apex. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389312/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389308>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Phanoperla wieng Sivec & Stark, 2010, male. a. Head and pronotum, dorsal view. b. Terminalia, dorsal view. c. Aedeagus, lateral view. d. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: a. 1 mm; b–d, 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389308/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

